   Duke J 1979 pp 95 [PH, RAIN, TEMP]
   Roecklein J 1987 pp 180 [USE]
   Bogdan A 1977 pp 175-181 [DRA, TEXT, RAIN]
   Kernick M 1961 pp 320
   Tropical forages 2005

